The most fun I've had <!--EZCODE ITALIC START--><em>PvP</em><!--EZCODE ITALIC END--> was in <!--EZCODE ITALIC START--><em>Arena</em><!--EZCODE ITALIC END-->, when the guild did a series of free-for-alls.  I was the sole survivor of caster/hybrid versus melee/priest, and eventually, they just had the entire guild gang up on me.<br>
