What I had done was arrive early and bind on top of one of the pillars inside the arena.  I chained pets at them, with the occasional nuke, but mostly I ran around, levved and on horseback, from pillar top to pillar top, gating away if anyone got too close.  Then I would go invisible, losing anyone who had me targeted, send out another pet, and bind wounds until I was ready to run around some more.<br>
<br>
